Changes to Clock
================

0.1.11
------
Fixed bug in repeating alarms.

0.1.10
------
Fixed bug concealing text label.  Fixed bug in update code.
Some clock face display tweaks.

0.1.9
-----
Added repeating alarms.
Can have the menu on the applet version.

0.1.8
-----
Rudimentary alarm facility.

0.1.7
-----
Support new AppInfo.xml data, debug output off by default.

0.1.6
-----
Re-organised the configuration of the app.  Some tweaks to the display.

0.1.5
-----
Added some locale handling.

0.1.4
-----
More display styles, including a user defined one.

0.1.3
-----
Added different display styles, and a configuration window to choose one.

0.1.2
-----
Corrected hour hand.

0.1.1
-----
Added info window
